messages.content:
Analyze the following browsing activity data for the user:

Top Categories:
{top_categories}

Top Topics:
{top_topics}

Sample Descriptions:
{sample_descriptions}

Generate a detailed browsing activity report addressed to the user (using 'you'/'your'). Use standard Markdown headings (using level 2 '##' or level 3 '###' syntax at the start of the line) to create sections for 'Overview', 'Key Themes', 'Notable Topics', and 'Category Focus'. Ensure the heading text itself does not contain the '#' characters. Provide insights based on the data. Ensure the output is only the valid Markdown report content.
